query:
SELECT
                SUM(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (e2.created_at - e1.created_at))) AS total_seconds
            FROM
                uptime_reports e1
            JOIN
                uptime_reports e2 ON e1.created_at < e2.created_at
            AND
                ABS(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (e1.created_at - e2.created_at))) <= 60
            AND
                e1.user_id = $1
            AND
                e2.user_id = $1
            AND
                e1.created_at >= $2
